AVERMEDIA INFO said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 40.05% to NT$85,601,000 from NT$142,792,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales             85,601          142,792    
YOY%             -40.05%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,661,543        2,297,755   
YOY%             -27.69% 
=================================================================
 